{"tid":526921,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"曾志偉執導筒放任女演員被強暴","createTime":"2018-01-12T06:25:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-12T18:00:35.000Z","uid":113626,"like":107,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"985057922b0d1e5f37c1c2ac08d403e4ef850d9f","tid":526921,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T06:25:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img-s-msn-com.akamaized.net/tenant/amp/entityid/AAuzZ7n.img?h=410&amp;w=728&amp;m=6&amp;q=60&amp;o=f&amp;l=f&amp;x=630&amp;y=312\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg-s-msn-com.akamaized.net%2Ftenant%2Famp%2Fentityid%2FAAuzZ7n.img%3Fh%3D410%26w%3D728%26m%3D6%26q%3D60%26o%3Df%26l%3Df%26x%3D630%26y%3D312&h=a4595236&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一則採訪藍潔瑛的視頻近日將男星曾志偉推上了風口浪尖，隨後，「模特兒教母」韓穎華也指控曾志偉「不止一次性侵女藝人」。日前有爆料再指，女星余倩文息影也是因為曾志偉。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，余倩文早年拍攝電影《安樂戰場》時，有一場強暴戲，片中男演員假戲真做，作為導演的曾志偉沒喊停，拍完後余倩雯痛苦萬分，同劇組的女美術指導也憤怒大罵曾志偉沒人性，隨後這段強暴戲被刪除，但余倩雯卻因此退出娛樂圈。對此，曾志偉則表示他誤以為余倩雯全情投入。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n赤裸和女兒視頻<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n此外，曾志偉上內地一檔訪談節目的一段截圖被挖出，好友和女兒曾寶儀分別爆料他愛全身脫光上廁所，且曾志偉和女兒曾寶儀視頻時也赤裸上身。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 娛樂圈大毒瘤"},{"pid":"ad55af16ff031e2ba31b885f2cd9651d41b34383","tid":526921,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T06:29:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f521212ed3ab0bf67dbaa207dbf54a217be98c79","tid":526921,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T06:32:28.000Z","msg":"真的嗎"},{"pid":"29243189feaf48e0505136dae62187fe64dab86a","tid":526921,"uid":121249,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T06:38:35.000Z","msg":"Super!"},{"pid":"3e1a9cd48defb1205d17a33dde6d2cc713506a79","tid":526921,"uid":65743,"like":0,"dislike":27,"score":-27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T06:40:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: 